{"id":104,"name":"Al-Humazah","nameArabic":"الهمزة","transliteration":"Al-Humazah","type":"meccan","ayahCount":9,"verses":[{"n":1,"text":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","translit":"Waylun likulli humazatin lumazatin","translation":"Woe to every scorner and mocker"},{"n":2,"text":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","translit":"Allathee jamaAAa malan waAAaddadahu","translation":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it"},{"n":3,"text":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","translit":"Yahsabu anna malahu akhladahu","translation":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal"},{"n":4,"text":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","translit":"Kalla layunbathanna fee alhutamati","translation":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher"},{"n":5,"text":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","translit":"Wama adraka ma alhutamatu","translation":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher"},{"n":6,"text":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","translit":"Naru Allahi almooqadatu","translation":"It is the fire of Allah, [eternally] fueled"},{"n":7,"text":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","translit":"Allatee tattaliAAu AAala alafidati","translation":"Which mounts directed at the hearts"},{"n":8,"text":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","translit":"lnnaha AAalayhim musadatun","translation":"Indeed, Hellfire will be closed down upon them"},{"n":9,"text":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","translit":"Fee AAamadin mumaddadatin","translation":"In extended columns"}]}